Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.44,0:00:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard, Keita.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.94,0:00:15.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The reason your house\Nis so loud lately...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.81,0:00:20.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...is because you're living\Nwith three pretty ladies.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.92,0:00:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Living with" isn't the right way to put it.\NThey're candidates to be my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.89,0:00:30.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're women who may\Nbecome my dad's wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.06,0:00:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that. And the fact\Nyou're to choose one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.47,0:00:40.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up, Keita!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.27,0:00:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I, Haruka Mikami, will run\Nas a mother candidate too!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.51,0:00:48.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.31,0:00:55.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like a Mom\NEpisode 2
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.49,0:00:58.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.19,0:01:02.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter.\NI choose to, so it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.16,0:01:06.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not. You'd be\Na candidate to be my mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.73,0:01:08.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.16,0:01:09.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you stupid?\NShut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.53,0:01:13.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make you\Nspeechless with my charm!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.27,0:01:15.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Speechless"...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.08,0:01:24.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be that you\Nwere in love with my dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.35,0:01:25.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.08,0:01:25.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?\NAre you serious, Haruka?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.98,0:01:27.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you serious, Haruka?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.32,0:01:29.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Taguchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.35,0:01:32.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You showed up, Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.96,0:01:36.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruka, is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.29,0:01:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.86,0:01:42.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, wonderful, Haruka.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.63,0:01:45.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm welcome to the idea, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.33,0:01:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up, Keita. She's one\Nof the candidates now as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.60,0:01:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get a room ready\Nfor her quickly, understood?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.01,0:01:55.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm off to work now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.71,0:01:57.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.28,0:01:59.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You too, Haruka!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.12,0:02:07.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell did he come here for?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.19,0:02:10.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for dinner,\NMiss Sawagiri. It was great.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.09,0:02:14.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiyo, you're a good cook.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.96,0:02:16.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.46,0:02:19.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. Haruka just\Nlocked herself in her room.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.10,0:02:22.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, I'm sure she's tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.54,0:02:26.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,True, she was irritated at carrying\Nher luggage all by herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.98,0:02:30.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's like my dad. She won't\Nquit once she's gotten started.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.98,0:02:35.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure she'll get bored of it right\Naway, so please look after her till then.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.72,0:02:38.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, please leave it to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.29,0:02:40.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, where's Noriko?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.56,0:02:43.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, she was\Nwandering around before...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.53,0:02:45.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you call?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.46,0:02:49.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was having dinner with Haruka.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.33,0:02:53.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A sports player eats\Nso much. I was amazed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.84,0:02:56.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, you have good taste, Chiyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.80,0:03:02.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sometimes order takeout from\Nthis place too, but it's always good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.18,0:03:04.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takeout?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.38,0:03:08.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, they listen\Nto your requests pretty well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.58,0:03:11.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's perfect for people like us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.85,0:03:13.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Noriko...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.36,0:03:15.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What, Kazuho?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.93,0:03:19.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Sawagiri!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.63,0:03:22.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiyo, we don't care about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.20,0:03:26.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Did I do something again?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.33,0:03:29.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Sawagiri,\Nplease wait! Miss Sawagiri!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.07,0:03:35.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Sawagiri, I don't\Ncare about stuff like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.41,0:03:38.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I always got takeout\Nwhen I was alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.51,0:03:43.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry that I can't be of\Nany help! I'm completely no-good!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.09,0:03:47.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying?\NYou're helping out a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.96,0:03:52.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't say such things.\NBecause of you, l...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.50,0:03:56.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A blackout?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.50,0:04:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's a blackout. Miss Sawagiri?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.50,0:04:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um, Keita, it's dark.\NI can't take the dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.84,0:04:08.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. It's just a blackout.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.21,0:04:11.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm scared.\NI'm scared of the dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.78,0:04:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you? I don't\Nlike being alone in the dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.62,0:04:18.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on. I'll come to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.82,0:04:19.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I stepped on something!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.89,0:04:21.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I stepped on something!\NKeita!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.99,0:04:23.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keita...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.73,0:04:27.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C-Chiyo, please don't\Ngrab hold of me like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.23,0:04:32.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keita... Keita... Keita...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.30,0:04:35.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Sawagiri, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.97,0:04:37.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.57,0:04:39.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keita...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.58,0:04:43.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't hurt yourself, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.58,0:04:47.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm bad with the dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.42,0:04:50.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm scared of it. I can't be alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.79,0:04:54.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right.\NI'm with you now after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.49,0:04:56.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Keita.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.33,0:05:00.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just glad I fell on the bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.83,0:05:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.70,0:05:03.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?\NDidn't you just call me by my first name?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.87,0:05:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you just call me by my first name?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.20,0:05:08.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did l? I'm very sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.07,0:05:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't misunderstand.\NIt made me happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.68,0:05:19.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since coming here, I was the only\None you didn't call by first name.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.21,0:05:22.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't like it because I felt alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.68,0:05:28.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, Keita, I want\Nto become closer to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.14,0:05:52.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Sawagiri, are you\Nsure you want to do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.45,0:05:54.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That won't do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.68,0:05:58.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That won't do.\NCall me by my first name.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.69,0:06:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Chiyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.52,0:06:04.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.75,0:06:32.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.33,0:06:43.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Keita...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.47,0:06:46.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.77,0:06:49.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait any longer...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.80,0:06:51.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, Chiyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.37,0:06:55.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I go. Huh? It's a little dark, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.81,0:06:59.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, Keita, that's my anus.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.05,0:07:01.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.28,0:07:02.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.88,0:07:05.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keita, it's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.19,0:07:08.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be nice to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.69,0:07:15.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine now. Please put it in.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.70,0:07:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay, Miss Sawagiri?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.01,0:07:28.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so mean. Use my first name.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.84,0:07:30.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Chiyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.01,0:08:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, don't tease it more than this! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.61,0:08:11.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say that. Let me hear more\Nof your sweet voice, Miss Sawagiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.69,0:08:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say it again... Say my name, Keita!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.86,0:08:20.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you have to be\Nturned on a little more.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.53,0:08:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't be mean, Keita.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.15,0:08:46.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keita, l... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.95,0:08:48.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keita!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.66,0:08:51.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, you're adorable, Chiyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.53,0:08:56.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please call me\Nby my first name again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.40,0:08:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.10,0:08:57.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiyo.\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.03,0:08:58.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.53,0:08:59.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiyo.\NYes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.72,0:09:21.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiyo...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.72,0:09:23.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keita...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.40,0:09:34.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'll be going.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.24,0:09:36.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, have a good day, Chiyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.10,0:09:39.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have a good day!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.37,0:09:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keita, you called\NChiyo by her first name.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.38,0:09:46.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.65,0:09:48.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing did.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.25,0:09:51.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure?\NIt seems kind of suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.92,0:09:56.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, it's weird only\Ncalling Chiyo by her last name.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.69,0:10:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you start today?\NThat's kind of weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.70,0:10:02.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.36,0:10:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen yesterday?\NHaruka!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.20,0:10:04.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing really.\NHaruka!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.20,0:10:04.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing really.\NNoriko.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.97,0:10:06.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After the lights went out, we just\Nwaited for them to come on.\NNoriko.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.23,0:10:09.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After the lights went out, we just\Nwaited for them to come on.\NThose two are close, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.14,0:10:10.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're sure?\NAs a candidate for his mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.81,0:10:11.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure.\NAs a candidate for his mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.87,0:10:13.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're really sure?\NDoesn't look that way to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.57,0:10:14.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am.\NDoesn't look that way to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.21,0:10:21.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what did you want to ask me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.08,0:10:25.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's not really\Nsomething I wanted to ask...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.92,0:10:30.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was wondering if you still\Nwanted to become Keita's mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.49,0:10:35.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I do. Why do you ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.00,0:10:40.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure someone becoming his\Nmother should do something like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.50,0:10:43.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was wondering\Nwhat you thought about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.07,0:10:50.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is from the other\Nday when Keita and l...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.85,0:10:52.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.65,0:10:55.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think\Nof my detective skills?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.85,0:10:59.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This wasn't like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.55,0:11:02.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're mistaken.\NI wasn't trying to do that...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.09,0:11:08.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I think it would be fine\Nif everyone became close.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.27,0:11:17.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazuho, the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.44,0:11:23.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, Taguchi residence.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.81,0:11:26.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,J-Jinta? No, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.68,0:11:28.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.98,0:11:31.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.75,0:11:33.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.92,0:11:35.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm at the beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.36,0:11:40.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to see it on my way home.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.63,0:11:45.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's wonderful. It's like the ocean\Nbreeze is cleansing my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.20,0:11:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, how's Keita doing?\NHas he slacked off all summer break?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.31,0:11:59.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, he's doing fine.\NHe worries about us every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.95,0:12:02.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was a blackout yesterday...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.05,0:12:07.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but it seems he was\Nlooking out for the neighborhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.76,0:12:11.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it seems like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.39,0:12:16.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Noriko, please stop that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.56,0:12:18.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just keep on talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.73,0:12:20.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.30,0:12:22.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.94,0:12:26.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, um... That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.51,0:12:27.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.71,0:12:30.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like it was trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.21,0:12:34.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Glad to hear Keita is being helpful.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.28,0:12:35.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.02,0:12:41.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rather than us being mothers to him,\Nhe's taking care of us instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.49,0:12:45.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that's not a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.23,0:12:52.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, the waves are loud here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.37,0:12:56.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm very grateful to you ladies.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.20,0:12:59.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Especially you, for\Ntaking care of the cooking...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.91,0:13:03.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...since Chiyo can't cook\Ntoo well, despite appearances.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.88,0:13:06.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jinta, you knew?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.88,0:13:09.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seemed Chiyo was\Ntrying to hide it, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.08,0:13:11.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yesterday too...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.42,0:13:16.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, i-it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.86,0:13:18.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.43,0:13:23.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I didn't know at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.90,0:13:30.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just thought she was a cute person\Ninside. That's what I realized recently.
